### Final Verdict & Next Steps
This is one of the cleanest AI-agent architectures I’ve reviewed. The core philosophy is genuinely innovative and the security/cost controls are excellent. Implement the four critical fixes and the five gaps above (especially the output manifest and orchestrator/engine boundary clarification), and you’ll have a system that can actually ship reliable code from a single prompt without the usual AI chaos.

